Class JIPipeNodeTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.api.JIPipeNodeTemplate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JIPipeParameterCollection

    public class JIPipeNodeTemplate
extends Object
implements JIPipeParameterCollection
    Contains the JSON data of a node that can be created by a user for sharing An intermediate between copying a node and a proper plugin.
